{"title":"都市盲道","authors":["姚焕吉"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"都市盲道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姚焕吉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条盲人之道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与大街并行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲道路面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有凸有凹　有凹有凸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像长长的盲文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲文写就的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用双脚默读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时会出现断章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或被节删"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是在交叉路口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以连贯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读不到的文字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由一根竹竿点击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出生命的网络"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲人在盲道上缓行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听身边车流如水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人流如水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而自己是一朵溅出的浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲人用心感受色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲人用手抚摸阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲人用眼洞察黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲道无阻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲道有限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁着眼的行人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不妨也闭上双目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在盲道上阅读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摔跤之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再睁开眼睛看书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定能读懂深奥的人生"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}